    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car has been pampered since day one and still has that fresh showroom smell! The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate a ride that\u2019s basically brand new. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how perfect it is!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
